data.description: Amazing recently renovated corner unit with beautiful partial lake view and garden. This 2bed/2bath unit has a brand-new kitchen, including stainless steel appliances, and beautiful quartz countertops. Beautiful new vinyl floors on both bedrooms. Master bedroom includes large walk-in closet. New vanities in both bathrooms. Washer/dryer hookup. Enjoy your evenings in your charming closed up patio while appreciating your garden/lake view. This active 55+ community offers 2 heated pools, gym, tennis court, library, sauna and clubhouse. Close to shopping, dining and highways.
